snippet.title: 11 Things That Have Changed In No Man's Sky Since Launch [ESRB]
snippet.description:
What's changed in No Man's Sky since launch? Well... Quite a lot actually. There are a lot more than 11 things, (see below) but we just wanted to highlight a few of our favourite things!

https://www.nomanssky.com/foundation-update/
https://www.nomanssky.com/pathfinder-update/
https://www.nomanssky.com/atlas-rises-update/

It's an incredibly exciting time for the folks at Hello Games, with No Man’s Sky and their NEXT update coming to Xbox One later this month! 

No Man’s Sky is available to pre-order NOW from in-store retailers on Xbox One. 

What’s more, pre-order the physical copy at GameStop and receive an X.O. Suit, a Starting Boost and the Artios-VI… 

https://www.gamestop.com/xbox-one/games/no-mans-sky/161089

For behind the scenes details on all of 505's games, head to the official 505 Games Blog: http://www.505games.com/blog
